{
  "stem": "18294.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 222.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And a lot of us was very, very sick.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Then the Russians come.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they're passing through, and they see we have an empty room.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They went in.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They wanted to sleep over.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So we were so lucky.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Everywhere was a Jew, and we was lucky.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So there was one from the manager from the Russian army, there was a Jew.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And he-- the Russians start to go to the girls, see girls, nothing.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We need a woman.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And we start to scream.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then he wake up, and he give it to them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "To who are you going?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The people are sick with typhus.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What you are looking with them?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The hell we went there through with the Russians.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So, you're in the township of Lauenburg.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Did you think of-- did you think of losing hope at any stage?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I said, when they come to this tent, and I said when I went through so much and I'm still alive, I'm going to find my husband.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And from there, we had no connection to Vilna back.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Just I had-- the 2-3 girls where they live in the-- little country behind Vilna.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we know how to do with a horse and carriage.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we took- we could take from the German everything then, everything what we wanted.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we took a horse.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was no trains.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was no connection to go there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Everything was-- the war wasn't finished.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The-- the Russians were there, but we couldn't do nothing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we took the horse and the carriage, and we was going a long way, till we come in-- in water so deep that the horse couldn't take us out.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we left the horse and the carriage, and we start to walk.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
